@api = http://localhost:8000/api

### Create issue
POST {{api}}/issues
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Checkout flow fails for VAT invoices",
  "description": "Enterprise users report timeout while submitting VAT invoice details in checkout from EU region.",
  "priority": "high",
  "category": "payments",
  "status": "open"
}

### List issues with filters
GET {{api}}/issues?status=open&priority=high

### View issue
GET {{api}}/issues/1

### Update issue
PATCH {{api}}/issues/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "in_progress",
  "priority": "critical"
}
